  notes:
    - "itertools.combinations_with_replacement.__name__ == 'combinations_with_replacement' (len=29); __module__ == 'itertools'; __qualname__ == 'combinations_with_replacement'; verified with Python 3.14.3."
    - "itertools.pairwise is available in Python 3.10+; pairwise.__name__ == 'pairwise' (len=8); pairwise.__module__ == 'itertools'; pairwise.__qualname__ == 'pairwise'; verified with Python 3.14.3."
    - "itertools.batched is available in Python 3.12+; batched.__name__ == 'batched' (len=7); batched.__module__ == 'itertools'; batched.__qualname__ == 'batched'; verified with Python 3.14.3."
